Task: Cook
Subtasks:
- Gather all necessary ingredients.
- Prepare the ingredients as needed (e.g., chop, peel).
- Cook the ingredients according to the recipe.
- Serve the meal.

Task: Place the red block on the blue block
Subtasks:
- Locate the red block.
- Grasp the red block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the blue block while holding the red block.
- Position the red block directly above the blue block.
- Carefully lower the red block onto the blue block.
- Release your grip on the red block, ensuring it is stable on the blue block.

Task: Place the red block on the plate
Subtasks:
- Locate the red block.
- Grasp the red block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the red block.
- Position the red block directly above the plate.
- Carefully lower the red block onto the plate.
- Release your grip on the red block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.

Task: Move the red block onto the plate, the blue block onto the red block, and the green block on the blue block
Subtasks:
- Locate the red block.
- Grasp the red block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the red block.
- Carefully position the red block on the center of the plate.
- Release your grip on the red block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.
- Locate the blue block.
- Grasp the blue block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the red block on the plate while holding the blue block.
- Position the blue block directly above the red block.
- Lower the blue block onto the red block.
- Release your grip on the blue block, ensuring it is stable on the red block.
- Locate the green block.
- Grasp the green block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the blue block on the red block while holding the green block.
- Position the green block directly above the blue block.
- Lower the green block onto the blue block.
- Release your grip on the green block, ensuring it is stable on the blue block.

- Lift the red block
- Locate the green block
- Move to the green block

Task: Stack the blocks on the plate
Subtasks:
- Locate the first block you intend to stack.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the block.
- Position the block directly above the center of the plate.
- Lower the block onto the plate.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.
- Locate the next block.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate and the previously placed block while holding the new block.
- Position this block directly above the first block on the plate.
- Carefully lower the block onto the first block.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the first block.

Task: Place the blue block on the yellow block
Subtasks:
- Locate the blue block.
- Grasp the blue block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the yellow block while holding the blue block.
- Position the blue block directly above the yellow block.
- Carefully lower the blue block onto the yellow block.
- Release your grip on the blue block, ensuring it is stable on the yellow block.

- Record the video.
- Edit the video.
- Add titles and captions.
- Publish the video.

Subtasks:

- Create an outline.
- Write the blog post.

- Proofread and edit the post.
- Publish the post.

Task: Place the red block on the blue block
Subtasks:
- Locate the red block.
- Grasp the red block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the blue block while holding the red block.
- Position the red block directly above the blue block.
- Carefully lower the red block onto the blue block.
- Release your grip on the red block, ensuring it is stable on the blue block.

Task: Place the red block on the plate
Subtasks:
- Locate the red block.
- Grasp the red block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the red block.
- Position the red block directly above the plate.
- Carefully lower the red block onto the plate.
- Release your grip on the red block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.

Task: Move the red block onto the plate, the blue block onto the red block, and the green block on the blue block
Subtasks:
- Locate the red block.
- Grasp the red block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the red block.
- Carefully position the red block on the center of the plate.
- Release your grip on the red block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.
- Locate the blue block.
- Grasp the blue block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the red block on the plate while holding the blue block.
- Position the blue block directly above the red block.
- Lower the blue block onto the red block.
- Release your grip on the blue block, ensuring it is stable on the red block.
- Locate the green block.
- Grasp the green block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the blue block on the red block while holding the green block.
- Position the green block directly above the blue block.
- Lower the green block onto the blue block.
- Release your grip on the green block, ensuring it is stable on the blue block.

Task: Place the red block on top of the green block.
Subtasks:
- Locate the red block
- Move towards the red block
- Grasp the red block
- Lift the red block
- Locate the green block
- Move to the green block

Task: Place the blue block on top of the yellow block.
Subtasks:
- stack the blue block on top of the yellow block, Locate the blue block
- Move towards the blue block
- Grasp the blue block
- Lift the blue block
- Locate the yellow block
- Move to the yellow block

Subtasks:

- Move towards the green block
- Grasp the green block
- Lift the green block

- Move to the blue block

Task: Stack the blocks on the plate
Subtasks:
- Locate the first block you intend to stack.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the block.
- Position the block directly above the center of the plate.
- Lower the block onto the plate.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.
- Locate the next block.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate and the previously placed block while holding the new block.
- Position this block directly above the first block on the plate.
- Carefully lower the block onto the first block.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the first block.

Task: Place the blue block on the yellow block
Subtasks:
- Locate the blue block.
- Grasp the blue block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the yellow block while holding the blue block.
- Position the blue block directly above the yellow block.
- Carefully lower the blue block onto the yellow block.
- Release your grip on the blue block, ensuring it is stable on the yellow block.

Task: Place the green block on the red block

- Move towards the red block while holding the green block.
- Position the green block directly above the red block.
- Carefully lower the green block onto the red block.

- Bake the cake for the specified time.

- Adjust expenses as needed to ensure savings.
- Review the budget monthly.

Subtasks:
- Choose a cause or charity.
- Set a fundraising goal.
- Plan fundraising activities.
- Create promotional materials.
- Reach out to potential donors.
- Host the fundraiser.
- Collect and manage donations.

Task: Plan a project
Subtasks:
- Define project objectives.
- Create a project timeline.
- Identify resources needed.
- Assign tasks to team members.
- Monitor progress.
- Adjust the plan as needed.
- Evaluate the project's success upon completion.

Task: Prepare a meal
Subtasks:
- Choose a recipe.
- Gather ingredients.
- Prepare ingredients (chop, measure, etc.).
- Cook according to the recipe instructions.
- Set the table.
- Serve the meal.
- Clean up afterward.

Task: Decorate a room
Subtasks:
- Choose a theme or color scheme.
- Select furniture and decor items.
- Arrange furniture in the room.
- Hang pictures or wall art.
- Add decorative touches (throw pillows, rugs, etc.).
- Ensure the room is functional and aesthetically pleasing.

Task: Host a webinar
Subtasks:
- Choose a topic.
- Select a date and time.
- Promote the webinar.
- Prepare the presentation.
- Test webinar software.
- Host the webinar.
- Follow up with participants afterward.

Task: Prepare a tax return
Subtasks:
- Gather financial documents.
- Choose a tax preparation method.
- Enter income information.
- Deduct expenses and claim credits.
- Review the return for accuracy.
- File the tax return.
- Keep a copy of the filed return for records.

- Identify target market.
- Design a survey or questionnaire.
- Collect data through surveys, interviews, or focus groups.
- Analyze data.
- Report findings.
- Make recommendations based on the research.

- Develop strategies based on the analysis.

Task: Place the red block on the blue block
Subtasks:
- Locate the red block.
- Grasp the red block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the blue block while holding the red block.
- Position the red block directly above the blue block.
- Carefully lower the red block onto the blue block.
- Release your grip on the red block, ensuring it is stable on the blue block.

- Move towards the yellow block

Task: Stack the blocks on the plate
Subtasks:
- Locate the first block you intend to stack.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the block.
- Position the block directly above the center of the plate.
- Lower the block onto the plate.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.
- Locate the next block.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate and the previously placed block while holding the new block.
- Position this block directly above the first block on the plate.
- Carefully lower the block onto the first block.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the first block.

Task: Place the blue block on the yellow block
Subtasks:
- Locate the blue block.
- Grasp the blue block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the yellow block while holding the blue block.
- Position the blue block directly above the yellow block.
- Carefully lower the blue block onto the yellow block.
- Release your grip on the blue block, ensuring it is stable on the yellow block.

Task: Place the green block on the red block
Subtasks:
- Locate the green block.
- Grasp the green block securely with your hand.

Task: Clean the windows
Subtasks:
- Gather cleaning supplies.
- Fill a bucket with water and window cleaner.
- Use a sponge to wash the windows.
- Use a squeegee to remove excess water.
- Wipe the edges of the window with a dry cloth.

Task: Organize the bookshelf
Subtasks:
- Remove all books from the shelf.
- Dust the shelves.
- Sort books by category or author.
- Place books back on the shelf in the chosen order.
- Adjust books to be evenly spaced.

Task: Mow the lawn
Subtasks:
- Check the lawnmower for fuel and oil.
- Adjust the cutting height on the lawnmower.
- Mow the lawn in straight lines.
- Empty the grass catcher when full.
- Clean the lawnmower after use.

Task: Bake a cake
Subtasks:
- Preheat the oven.
- Gather all ingredients.
- Mix dry ingredients together.
- Beat wet ingredients in a separate bowl.
- Combine dry and wet ingredients and pour into a baking pan.
- Bake the cake for the specified time.

Task: Do the laundry
Subtasks:
- Sort clothes by color.
- Add detergent to the washing machine.
- Load clothes into the machine.
- Set the washing machine cycle.
- Transfer clothes to the dryer.
- Fold and put away clothes after drying.

Task: Wash the dishes
Subtasks:
- Scrape food off dishes.
- Rinse dishes with water.
- Load dishes into the dishwasher.
- Add dishwasher detergent.
- Run the dishwasher.
- Unload and put away clean dishes.

Task: Vacuum the house
Subtasks:
- Plug in the vacuum cleaner.
- Vacuum all carpeted areas.
- Use attachments to clean corners and edges.
- Vacuum under furniture.
- Empty the vacuum cleaner bag or canister.

Task: Prepare a presentation
Subtasks:
- Choose a topic.
- Research the topic.
- Create an outline.
- Design slides using presentation software.
- Practice delivering the presentation.
- Make any necessary adjustments.

Task: Write a report
Subtasks:
- Gather all relevant information.
- Create an outline for the report.
- Write the introduction.
- Write the body of the report.
- Write the conclusion.
- Proofread and edit the report.

Task: Plan a party
Subtasks:
- Set a date and time.
- Create a guest list.
- Send out invitations.
- Plan the menu.
- Decorate the venue.
- Organize games and activities.

Task: Create a budget
Subtasks:
- List all sources of income.
- List all expenses.
- Categorize expenses (e.g., rent, groceries, entertainment).
- Calculate the difference between income and expenses.
- Adjust expenses as needed to ensure savings.
- Review the budget monthly.

Task: Build a website
Subtasks:
- Choose a domain name.
- Register the domain name.
- Select a web hosting service.
- Design the website layout.
- Write content for the website.
- Publish the website and test functionality.

Task: Paint a room
Subtasks:
- Choose paint color.
- Purchase paint and supplies.
- Move furniture out of the room.
- Cover floors and furniture with drop cloths.
- Tape off trim and edges.

Task: Stack the blocks on the plate
Subtasks:
- Locate the first block you intend to stack.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the block.
- Position the block directly above the center of the plate.
- Lower the block onto the plate.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.
- Locate the next block.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate and the previously placed block while holding the new block.
- Position this block directly above the first block on the plate.
- Carefully lower the block onto the first block.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the first block.

Task: Clean the windows
Subtasks:
- Gather cleaning supplies.
- Fill a bucket with water and window cleaner.
- Use a sponge to wash the windows.
- Use a squeegee to remove excess water.
- Wipe the edges of the window with a dry cloth.

Task: Organize the bookshelf
Subtasks:
- Remove all books from the shelf.
- Dust the shelves.
- Sort books by category or author.
- Place books back on the shelf in the chosen order.
- Adjust books to be evenly spaced.

Task: Mow the lawn
Subtasks:
- Check the lawnmower for fuel and oil.
- Adjust the cutting height on the lawnmower.
- Mow the lawn in straight lines.
- Empty the grass catcher when full.
- Clean the lawnmower after use.

Task: Bake a cake
Subtasks:
- Preheat the oven.
- Gather all ingredients.
- Mix dry ingredients together.
- Beat wet ingredients in a separate bowl.
- Combine dry and wet ingredients and pour into a baking pan.
- Bake the cake for the specified time.

Task: Do the laundry
Subtasks:
- Sort clothes by color.
- Add detergent to the washing machine.
- Load clothes into the machine.
- Set the washing machine cycle.
- Transfer clothes to the dryer.
- Fold and put away clothes after drying.

Subtasks:
- Scrape food off dishes.
- Rinse dishes with water.
- Load dishes into the dishwasher.
- Add dishwasher detergent.
- Run the dishwasher.
- Unload and put away clean dishes.

Task: Place the red block on the blue block
Subtasks:
- Locate the red block.
- Grasp the red block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the blue block while holding the red block.
- Position the red block directly above the blue block.
- Carefully lower the red block onto the blue block.
- Release your grip on the red block, ensuring it is stable on the blue block.

Task: Stack the blocks on the plate
Subtasks:
- Locate the first block you intend to stack.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the block.
- Position the block directly above the center of the plate.
- Lower the block onto the plate.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.
- Locate the next block.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate and the previously placed block while holding the new block.
- Position this block directly above the first block on the plate.
- Carefully lower the block onto the first block.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the first block.

Task: Stack the blocks on the plate
Subtasks:
- Locate the first block you intend to stack.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate while holding the block.
- Position the block directly above the center of the plate.
- Lower the block onto the plate.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the plate.
- Locate the next block.
- Grasp the block securely with your hand.
- Move towards the plate and the previously placed block while holding the new block.
- Position this block directly above the first block on the plate.
- Carefully lower the block onto the first block.
- Release your grip on the block, ensuring it is stable on the first block.
